# Schema registry — subjects, versions, and schema content
Output vhs/gifs/schema-registry.gif
Source vhs/_config.tape

Hide
Type "./kafui --mock --resource schemas" Enter
Sleep 3s
Show

Sleep 2500ms
Down@400ms 2
Sleep 1s
# Open schema detail
Enter
Sleep 2500ms
# Browse versions
Type "v"
Sleep 2500ms
Escape
Sleep 1200ms

Hide
Ctrl+C
